	measure 'Inventory-to-Budget Gap Ratio' = ```
			
			VAR _budget = [Fin. Budget Dynamic]
			VAR _orders = [Order In Period (Ext)]
			VAR _inv    = [Inventory Unrestricted Dynamic]    -- already excludes restricted inventory
			VAR _remaining_budget = _budget - _orders
			RETURN
			IF(
			    ISBLANK(_budget) || ISBLANK(_orders) || ISBLANK(_inv),
			    BLANK(),
			    DIVIDE(_inv, _remaining_budget)
			)
			
			```
