	measure 'Order In Period (Ext) test 1' = ```
			
			VAR _minSel = MINX(ALLSELECTED('g_dimdate_analytics_ipd'[CalendarDate]), 'g_dimdate_analytics_ipd'[CalendarDate])
			VAR _maxSel = MAXX(ALLSELECTED('g_dimdate_analytics_ipd'[CalendarDate]), 'g_dimdate_analytics_ipd'[CalendarDate])
			RETURN
			CALCULATE (
			    [Order In Dynamic (Ext) test 1],
			    -- kill active CreateDate filter from DimDate
			    REMOVEFILTERS ( g_bowler_orders[CreateDate] ),
			    -- use RequestedDeliveryDate for the current DimDate month
			    USERELATIONSHIP ( g_bowler_orders[_nkeyRequestedDeliveryDate], 'g_dimdate_analytics_ipd'[skeyDay] ),
			    -- window constraints
			    g_bowler_orders[CreateDate] <= _maxSel,
			    g_bowler_orders[RequestedDeliveryDate] >= _minSel,
			    g_bowler_orders[RequestedDeliveryDate] <= _maxSel
			)
			
			```
		displayFolder: Testing
		lineageTag: 0964e552-1ed6-4507-aa2a-054b4baead74

